        "text": "Growing and improving also means knowing how to look ahead.\n\nThis is why we proudly continue to pursue responsible business strategies, committing ourselves to building sustainable development and creating the best possible working environment for our stakeholders and future generations.\n\nWith the 2022-2030 Sustainability Plan we have defined the corporate strategy to strengthen our approach to Corporate Social Responsibility, contributing to reach the objectives of the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development of the United Nations (SDG).\n\nThe Plan, structured around six areas of action, is always updated based on the results achieved and new needs that emerge over time."
